title: 2013 Ratboy's Rodent Rampage
description:
The third annual Rat Boy's Rodent Rampage presented by O'Neill was once again met with perfect weather and great surf. 48 youthful competitors showed up at Steamer Lane on Saturday morning with competition on their minds after watching the O'Neill Coldwater Classic, which took place only three days prior. 


MICE (17 and under)
1. Wyatt Barrabee
2. Carlos Carpenter
3. Ritchie Schmidt
4. Ben Coffey


Pink Bellies (14 and Under)
1. Fisher Baxter
2. Sam Coffey
3. Aj Menna
4. Cory Svardal
